records.addlTxt:
1:31 PM Defendant Sierra M Alexander in court.  Attorney Daniel McGrath in court for State of Wisconsin. 
Officer Plowman is sworn in and testifies. Testifies to being dispatched to Daly Drug. Testifies to speaking with VC. Testifies to a prescription being called in with a doctors DEA number. Testifies to the DEA being the doctors actual number and him not giving anyone consent to use it. Testifies to the defendant being the one to going to get the prescription. Witness identifies the defendant in court, court recognizes. Testifies to the statement made by the defendant about why she was picking that prescription up. Testifies to the defendant giving him a Louisiana license and came back to a WP. Testifies to speaking with that person and him not giving anyone permission to use his DL. 

Court finds probable cause to believe a felony was committed and the defendant committed it.

Bond is continued.
Arraignment scheduled for July 25, 2022 at 10:00 am.
